Foxit Reader is free software while advanced add-ons have a reasonable cost. Actually you are still able to evaluate these functions. However when you save the edited document, it will be stamped with an evaluation mark on the top-right corner of the edited pages. If you purchase the corresponding add-ons, then there will be no evaluation marks.
